translations.name: Our Lord and Saviour Jesus Christ's New Testament
translations.description: Vor Herres og Frelseres Jesu Christi Nyw Testamente: The Vor Herres og Frelseres Jesu Christi Nyw Testamente is a Danish New Testament published by the British Foreign Bible Society in 1827. The American Bible Society published a second edition in 1914.
